OL,5, Former ITN chief executive John Hardie 
OL,6, is to lead an independent review of BBC
OL,7, social media guidelines in the wake of 
OL,8, the furore over Gary Lineker's tweets. 
OL,10,FThe row erupted when the Match of the  
OL,11,FDay host said the government's language
OL,12,Fabout migrants was "not dissimilar to  
OL,13,Fthat used by Germany in the 30s".      
OL,15,FHe was taken off air for breaching the 
OL,16,FBBC's guidelines on impartiality.      
OL,18,FBut he returned a week later, with the 
OL,19,Fthe corporation announcing the review  
OL,20,Fto address "grey areas" in its rules.  
